nhc_headline: ...IMELDA MOVING AWAY FROM THE BAHAMAS... ...FORECAST TO BECOME A HURRICANE ON TUESDAY OR TUESDAY NIGHT...
summary: ...IMELDA MOVING AWAY FROM THE BAHAMAS... ...FORECAST TO BECOME A HURRICANE ON TUESDAY OR TUESDAY NIGHT... As of 11:00 PM EDT Mon Sep 29 the center of Imelda was located near 28.4, -77.2 with movement N at 8 mph. The minimum central pressure was 987 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 65 mph.
